title: 03/09/22 DPS Hour 2 Booger McFarland
itunes:title: 03/09/22 DPS Hour 2 Booger McFarland
description:
Booger McFarland tells Dan that it would be a travesty for Aaron Rodgers to win 4 MVP's and only have 1 Super Bowl appearance. Booger says that the pressure is on Rodgers more than Russell Wilson.
